<br>
I've never had a problem dealing with them, the companies provide their own warrenties, etc.<br>
<br>
If you prefer, sure, go to gateway.com or Frys Electronics or something like that and pay twice as much. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
